title: IMEI Number on the phone box and in Settings don't match. IMEI Check says it belongs to Samsung!?
content:
1. IMEI Number on the phone box and the one displayed in Settings don't match.

2. After checking the IMEI Number displayed in the Settings on https://www.imeipro.info/ it says it belongs to SAMSUNG and is Blacklisted. What's wrong with it? How is it possible? Means that that my Pixel 3a is not original?

Please HELP!!! Thanx.

P.S. Phone was bought in the US.
